{"id":1736876,"retrievedAt":"2026-07-24T12:40:14.574Z","response":{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":null,"belongs_to_collection":null,"budget":0,"genres":[],"homepage":"","id":1736876,"imdb_id":null,"origin_country":["US"],"original_language":"en","original_title":"Angkara Cinta","overview":"# Translation  The story tells of two men who happen to share the same name: Luqmanul Haqeem bin Razlan. Luqman and Haqeem grew up in very different family backgrounds. One was blessed with luxury while the other was trapped in poverty. As adults, fate brings them together as best friends and they enter the Police Academy together. They share everything, spending difficult and good times together, unaware that they are actually half-brothers sharing the same father. Mariani (Haqeem's mother) and Razlan married at the border, but Razlan fled when Mariani became pregnant with Haqeem. It turns out Razlan married Indah and had a son, Luqman. Razlan was forbidden by his mother to return to Mariani, and she fabricated a story that Mariani had miscarried. Eventually, after several incidents occur, the truth is finally revealed that Luqman and Haqeem are half-brothers. From then on, their relationship grows cold and various conflicts begin to emerge.","popularity":0,"poster_path":null,"production_companies":[{"id":97907,"logo_path":null,"name":"Juita Viden Sdn Bhd","origin_country":""}],"production_countries":[],"release_date":"2020-01-01","revenue":0,"runtime":0,"softcore":false,"spoken_languages":[],"status":"Released","tagline":"","title":"Angkara Cinta","video":false,"vote_average":0,"vote_count":0,"alternative_titles":{"titles":[]},"credits":{"cast":[{"adult":false,"gender":0,"id":2408155,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Hun Haqeem","original_name":"Hun Haqeem","popularity":0.6417,"profile_path":"/ZJ0iMK9B8bwOpVZ8pywTKdpugX.jpg","cast_id":2,"character":"","credit_id":"6a62ba42c3b9bdbdee04f6e3","order":0},{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":2975679,"known_for_department":"Acting","na